      @Deprecated public void spawnCreature​(org.bukkit.Location location)
      Deprecated.
      Overriden via the spawnCreature(Location, BarColor, BarStyle, BarFlag) method
      Using this method will break the creature and will no longer identify the creature as a boss. This renders the creation of a OBossCreature useless and redundant.
